description:
If you're looking for a great set of insightful School quotes - look no further.  School Quotes comes loaded with a huge number of phrases, jokes, sayings and messages so you will be always able to enjoy new quotes while you're on the go!

School Quotes offers a simple and attractive interface.  Simply tap or shake your Palm device and a new quote is displayed.  Or you can search through all the quotes in one comprehensive list and select the one you want to read.  It's great if you want to go back and review one particular quote.  Whichever way you choose to view, you'll enjoy hours of fulfillment reviewing these great quotes.

If you enjoy School discussions, you owe it to yourself to download School Quotes today!
